==English==
===Noun===
# {{particles}} A [[particle]] with totally antisymmetric composite [[quantum]] states, which means they must obey the Pauli exclusion principle, and that obey Fermi-Dirac statistics.  They have half-integer [[spin]].  Among them are many elementary particles, most derived from [[quark]]s.  All particles are either [[boson]]s or fermions.

====Antonym====
*[[boson]]

